# My-Direct.list
# Private direct whitelist - user's own domains/services
# Strategy: ADD ONLY - never block these
# ⚠️ Edit this file to add your own domains that should never be proxied

# === User Private Services (add your own here) ===
# Example:
# DOMAIN-SUFFIX,myhomepc.local
# DOMAIN-SUFFIX,mynas.local
# DOMAIN,homeassistant.local

# === Local Network ===
# DOMAIN-SUFFIX,local
# DOMAIN-SUFFIX,lan
# DOMAIN,localhost

# === Common Local Services ===
# DOMAIN,router.asus.com
# DOMAIN,192.168.1.1

# Add your custom domains below:
# DOMAIN-SUFFIX,yourdomain.com
# DOMAIN,yourservice.local